						<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary font-heading">PROFESSIONAL AC INSTALLATION</h2>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darkgray mb-6">
						EXPERT AIR CONDITIONING INSTALLATION SERVICES
					</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						When it comes to keeping your home cool and comfortable during the hot Texas summers, a properly installed
						air conditioning system is essential. At Alltek Services, we provide professional AC installation services
						for new construction, system replacements, and upgrades in Belton and the surrounding areas.
					</p>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Our team of certified technicians has extensive experience installing all types of air conditioning systems,
						including central air conditioners, ductless mini-splits, and high-efficiency units. We work with leading
						manufacturers to provide you with reliable, energy-efficient cooling solutions that fit your specific needs
						and budget.
					</p>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-8">
						From helping you select the right system size and type to ensuring proper installation and setup, our
						experts handle every aspect of the process with professionalism and attention to detail, ensuring your new
						AC system delivers optimal performance and comfort for years to come.
					</p>
